column18: BIS-BAS_1 - A person's family is the most important thing in life.
column19: BIS-BAS_1 - Even if something bad is about to happen to me, I rarely experience fear or nervousness.
column20: BIS-BAS_1 - I go out of my way to get things I want.
column21: BIS-BAS_1 - When I'm doing well at something I love to keep at it.
column22: BIS-BAS_1 - I'm always willing to try something new if I think it will be fun.
column23: BIS-BAS_1 - How I dress is important to me.
column24: BIS-BAS_1 - When I get something I want, I feel excited and energized.
column25: BIS-BAS_1 - Criticism or scolding hurts me quite a bit.
column26: BIS-BAS_1 - When I want something I usually go all out to get it.
column27: BIS-BAS_1 - I will often do things for no other reason than that they might be fun.
column28: BIS-BAS_1 - It's hard for me to find the time to do things such as get a haircut.
column29: BIS-BAS_1 - If I see a chance to get something I want I move on it right away.
column30: BIS-BAS_2 - I feel pretty worried or upset when I think or know somebody is angry at me.
column31: BIS-BAS_2 - When I see an opportunity for something I like I get excited right away.
column32: BIS-BAS_2 - I often act on the spur of the moment.
column33: BIS-BAS_2 - If I think something unpleasant is going to happen I usually get pretty "worked up."
column34: BIS-BAS_2 - I often wonder why people act the way they do.
column35: BIS-BAS_2 - When good things happen to me, it affects me strongly.
column36: BIS-BAS_2 - I feel worried when I think I have done poorly at something important.
column37: BIS-BAS_2 - I crave excitement and new sensations.
column38: BIS-BAS_2 - When I go after something I use a "no holds barred" approach.
column39: BIS-BAS_2 - I have very few fears compared to my friends.
column40: BIS-BAS_2 - It would excite me to win a contest.
column41: BIS-BAS_2 - I worry about making mistakes.
